{"word":"Sanctuary","slug":"sanctuary","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sanctuary</b> The holy of holies.<br/> In the tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse=2'>Heb 9:2</a><br/> Divine dwelling place<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=25&verse=8'>Exo 25:8</a><br/> Reverence for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=19&verse=30'>Lev 19:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=26&verse=2'>Lev 26:2</a><br/> High priest in charge of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=27&verse=21'>Exo 27:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=24&verse=3'>Lev 24:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=5'>Num 18:5</a><br/> The holy place in the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=2&verse=7'>Lam 2:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=2&verse=20'>Lam 2:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=42&verse=20'>Eze 42:20</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=11&verse=16'>Eze 11:16</a><br/> Symbolic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=8&verse=2'>Heb 8:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=8&verse=5'>Heb 8:5</a><br/><a href='S:Tabernacle'>Tabernacle</a>; <a href='S:Temple'>Temple</a>"}]}